data.description: Welcome to 88 Shire Drive. Located near everything the Wentzville/ Lake St Louis area has to offer this charming 2 story  Federal style home is ready for you. Freshly painted and newly carpeted this light and bright 3 bedroom, 2 and 1/2 bathroom has primary bedroom suite with huge bath and walk in closet. Custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances in your galley kitchen that opens into a large breakfast room with glass sliding doors and easy access to patio and backyard and your family room with fireplace, separate living and dining room complete the main floor. Two car garage, full basement. One year HSA home warranty included.
